{"tid":1318322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"示威者和警方在新城市廣場內衝突　28傷者中2人危殆","createTime":"2019-07-15T02:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T02:17:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d06831d022dd949a546505384f2ae89ec07fc4fe","tid":1318322,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"示威者和警方在新城市廣場內衝突　28傷者中2人危殆<br />\n<br />\n2019-07-15 HKT <br />\n<br />\n沙田反修訂《逃犯條例》遊行結束後，示威者及防暴警察昨晚在新城市廣場內發生衝突。多名示威者、警員及記者受傷。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局表示，事件中有28人受傷，其中22人仍然留院，兩人情況危殆、4人嚴重、14人情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，有10名警員受傷，其中一人被咬斷一截手指。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468403-20190715.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468403-20190715.htm&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKaEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=fc8e4280\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1468403-20190715.htm&h=47d51062\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1468403-20190715.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ce82695348835cc631ec89b51f3d96a36405a3e7","tid":1318322,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}